node.text:
🎿GIVEAWAY 🏂
@mabeyski is teaming up with @messyweekendco to give you a chance to win – there are two prizes up for grabs; a guided backcountry weekend in Whistler with @mabeyski and a pair of goggles from our friends at @messyweekendco.

 

 💥 PRIZES 💥

1st Prize – guided backcountry weekend in Whistler with @mabeyski

 

2nd Prize – pair of goggles from @messyweekendco

 

HOW TO ENTER 

1.  Make sure you are following both @messyweekendco and @mabeyski

 

2. Tag a buddy in the comments. Each new friend tagged counts as one entry.

 

1 tag = 1 comment = 1 entry

 

3.  Share to your story for 5 extra entries 

 

TERMS AND CONDITIONS 

Competition ends and prize winners will be drawn on 23 August.

Winners will be announced by a comment on this post and in @mabeyski stories.
